Class FileInclusionDirectiveConditionDateTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.softwareag.wx.is.config.directive.FileInclusionDirective
      • com.softwareag.wx.is.config.directive.FileInclusionDirectiveConditionDateTime

  • public class FileInclusionDirectiveConditionDateTime
extends FileInclusionDirective
    Handle (usually deferred) loading and unloading of file based on date/time conditions. One-time schedulers are created to perform this.
